{"tid":2089382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO移民 = 支持國際黃圈，破壞力極大","createTime":"2020-07-01T15:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T04:01:45.000Z","uid":267881,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eba02db510b5035c3416c73771e218d7269e9488","tid":2089382,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"手持BNO的禍港黃屍中產大多已到中年，身驕肉貴不敢違法，搭車食飯揀黃圈黎降低罪惡感，一個月貢獻幾千，已經好盡，一世先幾百萬。<br />\n<br />\n但交稅、買樓呢啲必要性支出涉款6～7位數，最大受益人係我們偉大祖國。<br />\n<br />\n但移民係不分黃藍，即時拎走幾百萬、幾千萬起跳，將錢同技能搬晒去黃色國家。<br />\n<br />\n所以移民只會係搬石頭砸自己祖國的腳，為香港經濟添煩添亂。<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要支持政府，支持國家，唔好走，堅守浪漫主義，幫國家渡過難關，希望高官可以身作則，放棄外國國籍。<br />\n<br />\n更甚者，如果俾班暴徒逃離香港，在國外繼續進行分裂中國行為，國安署將難以執法阻止，後果不堪設想。<br />\n<br />\n縱觀歷史，大多成功革命都係由流亡海外的份子策動，權衡輕重，我認為政府應鼓勵暴徒留港，方便監視，隨時輯拿正法，充公資產。<br />\n<br />\n中產留低有咩作為<br />\n中產移民有咩影響<br />\n諗清楚先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持港區國安法<br />\n支持反制外國勢力<br />\n認同請分享<br />\n不認同請拉"},{"pid":"627516ce0188ad0e72a1126a870d166145563ba6","tid":2089382,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔要繳稅養gestapo 起集中營"},{"pid":"d4c8176a9befa2727d947e776002a7ffbd1ea6f4","tid":2089382,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6726dc429d3fb681e10afc289738fb59e6145b21","tid":2089382,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cee8af56804b888ace169eba2bb5ceac55c1e2c","tid":2089382,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:50:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db3c983350b54bd1ad99820db90e317519c17359","tid":2089382,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8706b1378907d634478dbb7555642acdb36474bc","tid":2089382,"uid":304769,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"借個位，BNO平權正視聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑色五毛分化警告，大量五毛正在用藍絲有BNO、走人對唔住97後割97後等風向進行分化</span></span></strong>，大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比人拉過/有小朋友（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）的話就應該即刻走</span></span></strong>，其他人亦應該起碼做好隨時走既準備，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港抗爭運動已經由本土抗爭升級為準國際戰爭， 我們能做的十分有限。 相反大家離開或準備好隨時可以離開，則美國及其盟友可以隨時採取行動，對香港進行制裁，令香港達至零經濟活動，攬炒香港經濟， 甚至日後作出軍事行動亦無需擔心誤傷香港人。</span></span></strong> 而且大家亦可用移民理由提取所有資產及強積金進一步<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊香港的財政儲備</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而且多人走亦可以起到掩護最需要走既手足，救奶左野手足係目前最重要既事。<br />\n<br />\n2.大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無需擔心藍絲以及黑警移民英國</span></span></strong>，藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或推到現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望樓主可以pin，一齊擊退五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6d540772b8be687c6b46d2c9c450ae8f7c4c8080","tid":2089382,"uid":208689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T00:43:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f69893b83cc3cb3b1ea893694aee86ea012332e8","tid":2089382,"uid":68363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:06:58.000Z","msg":"Agree no more<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f20d03151fe95409eff09b172604ba238e7fba","tid":2089382,"uid":133383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"support <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8e5720affb5b6bd8686ec49063e7e6316d2e09","tid":2089382,"uid":27391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"afdc688a8fcf418e583d0ca013ed5eaabf04df73","tid":2089382,"uid":124616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:28:54.000Z","msg":"好似猶太人咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e37485bb8bab2a5376bccd3a4e590de6981aa6","tid":2089382,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afdc688a8fcf418e583d0ca013ed5eaabf04df73","tid":2089382,"uid":124616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:28:54.000Z","msg":"好似猶太人咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"香港人係龍係蟲自有分曉<br />\n但一定唔可以扼殺任何可能性"},{"pid":"d1c9e682509fa8de8d2877312d215fba59bad4dc","tid":2089382,"uid":3149,"like"